OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FA photographer from Dorset has been
OL,8,Fselected as the 2025 South West Coast
OL,9,FPath Photographer of the Year for a
OL,10,Fpicture of the cliffs at West Bay.
OL,12,FThe image, entitled Falling Fog, was
OL,13,Ftaken by Neil Barnes on a winter's
OL,14,Fmorning, and shows the cliffs softened
OL,15,Fby a veil of mist rolling across the
OL,16,Ficonic landscape.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FThe South West Coast Path Association
OL,8,F(SWCPA), the charity that cares for
OL,9,Fthe path, has been hosting the annual
OL,10,Fcompetition for 14 years. It attracts
OL,11,Fup to 1,500 entries and has been
OL,12,Fexpanded to include seven categories,
OL,13,Fplus a SWCP team pick.
OL,15,FSOUTH WEST COAST PATH PHOTOGRAPHER OF
OL,16,FTHE YEAR 2025
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FA panel of three judges were unanimous
OL,8,Fin their selection of the winning
OL,9,Fimage, including Jessica Lennan,
OL,10,FLecturer in Photography at Plymouth
OL,11,FUniversity, who had this to say of
OL,12,FNeil's image: "A beautiful view of the
OL,13,FDorset coast, where mist drifts gently
OL,14,Facross the cliffs, creating a profound
OL,15,Fsense of calm and openness. At first
OL,16,Fglance, the scene appears serene and
OL,17,Falmost timeless, but look a little
OL,18,Fcloser, and the signs of a recent
OL,19,Flandslide reveal the coastline's
OL,20,Funderlying fragility. It's a quiet
OL,21,Fimage that invites both admiration and
OL,22,Freflection, showing the coast as a
OL,23,Fplace of delicate balance and constant
OL,24,Ftransformation."
OL,26,@tD@OOU@E@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FWinning photographer Neil Barnes said:
OL,8,F"It was a particularly foggy morning
OL,9,Fas I walked with my dog Betsy to the
OL,10,Fend of the pier at West Bay. I could
OL,11,Fsee how the fog and mist were steadily
OL,12,Fmoving from the land at the top of the
OL,13,Fcliffs and spilling over down towards
OL,14,Fthe beach, an incredible sight to see.
OL,15,FAs I approach my fiftieth year as a
OL,16,Fphotographer, very occasionally, I get
OL,17,Fthat feeling of amazement and
OL,18,Fexcitement when I see something
OL,19,Fspecial, and this felt like a once-in-
OL,20,Fa-lifetime opportunity. I was
OL,21,Fabsolutely thrilled to be able to
OL,22,Fcapture it.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,F"I feel very humbled to have this
OL,8,Fpicture chosen as the overall winner
OL,9,Fand hope people get as much enjoyment
OL,10,Fand wonder at seeing it as I did when
OL,11,FI captured it."
OL,13,FThe winning image of the nature
OL,14,Fcategory was taken in Cornwall by Emma
OL,15,FEccles.
OL,26,@sD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FHeidi Morstand, Associate Professor in
OL,8,FPhotography at Plymouth University,
OL,9,Fsaid: "This beautifully composed image
OL,10,Fimmediately invites the viewer to
OL,11,Ffollow the path and step into the
OL,12,Fscene. The photographer's careful
OL,13,Farrangement of the elements creates a
OL,14,Fnatural flow through the frame,
OL,15,Fdrawing the eye gently toward the
OL,16,Fcoastline.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,F"The low light enhances the
OL,8,Fatmosphere, casting a soft, warm glow
OL,9,Fthat brings a delicate tenderness to
OL,10,Fthe landscape. The thrifts in full
OL,11,Fbloom add vibrancy and texture,
OL,12,Fevoking the richness of early summer.
OL,13,FAltogether, the photograph captures
OL,14,Fthe essence of warm, inviting days
OL,15,Falong the coast path`a serene and
OL,16,Fimmersive celebration of nature at its
OL,17,Fmost welcoming."
OL,19,FCLIMATE CHANGE
OL,26,@yD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/19
