OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FMarlena Ciach won the climate change
OL,8,Fcategory with her photo taken on
OL,9,FExmoor.
OL,11,FThe Director of the South West Coast
OL,12,FPath Association, Julian Gray, said:
OL,13,F"A great image showing the power of
OL,14,Fwater and the dynamic nature of our
OL,15,Fcoast. The high tide waters engulfing
OL,16,FPorlock Marsh indicate the threat of
OL,17,Frising sea levels to our coastal
OL,18,Flowlands."
OL,20,FPEOPLE AND PATH
OL,26,@zD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FThe people and path category award was
OL,8,Fgiven to Keith Mason for this
OL,9,FCoastwatch image.
OL,11,FJudge Jessica Lennan said: "A strong
OL,12,Fand engaging portrait that draws
OL,13,Fattention to the people who live and
OL,14,Fwork along the South West Coast Path.
OL,15,FIt offers a glimpse into the everyday
OL,16,Fpresence of those who help shape and
OL,17,Flook after this coastline."
OL,19,FThe winner of the wildlife category is
OL,20,FArchie Raistrick, with his image of a
OL,21,Fyoung badger in North Devon.
OL,26,@yD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
