OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FJudge Heidi Morstang said: "This
OL,8,Fphotograph offers an intimate and
OL,9,Fengaging portrait of a young badger in
OL,10,Fits natural habitat. The animal's
OL,11,Fdirect gaze creates an immediate
OL,12,Fconnection with the viewer, capturing
OL,13,Fa moment of curiosity that feels both
OL,14,Fgentle and quietly compelling.
OL,26,@oD@\OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,F"The surrounding wildflowers bring
OL,8,Fsubtle colour and texture to the
OL,9,Fscene, while the softness of the grass
OL,10,Fbeautifully frames the badger and
OL,11,Freinforces the sense of being immersed
OL,12,Fwithin its environment. The
OL,13,Fphotographer demonstrates a sensitive
OL,14,Funderstanding of wildlife observation,
OL,15,Fallowing the landscape to support
OL,16,Frather than overwhelm the subject.
OL,18,F"Altogether, this is a finely observed
OL,19,Fand atmospheric depiction`an intimate
OL,20,Fglimpse into the life of a badger in
OL,21,Fits natural world."
OL,26,@}D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
