PN,43112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FThe winning image taken from the sky
OL,8,Fis by George Cryer and shows Pedn
OL,9,FVounder beach.
OL,11,FJudge Julian Gray said: "This year, we
OL,12,Fhave seen more oblique sky shots
OL,13,Fentered into the competition. This
OL,14,Fevocative image of Pedn Vounder beach
OL,15,Ffrom the sky shows why this part of
OL,16,FCornwall inspires so many artists. The
OL,17,Fstrong colours and patterns in the
OL,18,Fwater contrast with the soft patterns
OL,19,Facross the sand. The cliffs rise
OL,20,Fstrongly with geometric strength. This
OL,21,Fimage provokes exploration."
OL,26,@sD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/19
