OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FURBAN LINES
OL,9,FThis photo of Lynmouth by Shaun Davey
OL,10,Fwon the urban lines category.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
