FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FJudge Jessica Lennan said: "You
OL,8,Fwouldn't normally think of Lynmouth in
OL,9,Fan urban category, yet this image
OL,10,Fmakes it work beautifully. Taken at
OL,11,Fdusk, just as the lights have switched
OL,12,Fon, there's a warm glow that runs
OL,13,Falong the houses, the seafront, and
OL,14,Fthe bridge, tracing the lines and
OL,15,Fshapes of the town. The photograph
OL,16,Fhighlights the geometry of the place,
OL,17,Fshowing a side of Lynmouth that feels
OL,18,Fboth familiar and freshly seen."
OL,20,FYOUNG PHOTOGRAPHER OF THE YEAR
OL,26,@oD@\OUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
