FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FSeventeen-year-old Arthur Allan won
OL,8,Fthe young photographer category with a
OL,9,Fpicture of choughs in West Cornwall.
OL,10,FThe birds are a symbol of Cornwall and
OL,11,Fbecame extinct in the Duchy in the
OL,12,F1970s before returning at the turn of
OL,13,Fthe century.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FJudge Heidi Morstang said: "This is a
OL,8,Fcharming and sensitively observed
OL,9,Fimage, capturing two resting choughs
OL,10,Fnestled among wildflowers. The
OL,11,Fphotographer has made excellent use of
OL,12,Fcolour and texture: the rich tones of
OL,13,Fthe birds stand out beautifully
OL,14,Fagainst the soft carpet of blooms,
OL,15,Fcreating a striking yet gentle visual
OL,16,Fcontrast.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,F"The scene feels intimate and
OL,8,Fcarefully noticed, offering a quiet
OL,9,Fmoment of connection with these
OL,10,Fdistinctive coastal birds. The framing
OL,11,Fenhances this closeness, allowing the
OL,12,Fviewer to appreciate both the birds
OL,13,Fthemselves and the delicate
OL,14,Fenvironment they inhabit. It is a
OL,15,Fthoughtful and beautifully executed
OL,16,Fphotograph, demonstrating impressive
OL,17,Fobservational skill from a young
OL,18,Fphotographer."
OL,20,FSOUTH WEST COAST PATH TEAM PICK
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
