OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775049066
OL,3,CWinning images of the South West Coast
OL,4,CPath Photographer of the Year
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FThis sunset photo by Charisse Wold in
OL,8,FSouth Devon was the SWCP team pick
OL,9,Fthis year.
OL,11,FSWCP National Trail Officer Lorna
OL,12,FSherriff said: "When I first saw this
OL,13,Fimage, it immediately drew me in, and
OL,14,FI felt as though I was sitting on the
OL,15,Fcoast, experiencing the sunset myself.
OL,16,FIt conveys a strong sense of
OL,17,Ftranquillity and peace, capturing a
OL,18,Fmagical moment as the young person
OL,19,Frelaxes and connects with the coast,
OL,20,Fcreating a lasting memory."
OL,26,@|D@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/19
